{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/913740/extras/WOHstorewashi-export.png?t=1730740660\" /><br><br>The Old Gods are reawakening, clawing their way back into a world that\u2019s spiraling into madness. In hospitals, abandoned classrooms, quiet apartments, and dark forests, strange appearances and unexplainable phenomena test the sanity of residents in Shiokawa, Japan. Is it chaotic retribution, or the machinations of beings beyond our comprehension?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/913740/extras/Final_GIF1.gif?t=1730740660\" /><br><br>This is WORLD OF HORROR: The end of the world is nigh, and the only solution is to confront the terror reigning over the apocalypse. Navigate this hellish, roguelite reality through turn-based combat and unforgiving choices in this roguelite-style cosmic horror RPG.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/913740/extras/Final_GIF2.gif?t=1730740660\" /><br><br>Invoke dark rituals, uncover disturbing clues, and solve puzzles across multiple randomized mysteries. Each perplexing case unravels into a series of random encounters with nightmarish figures inspired by the works of horror legends Junji Ito and H.P. Lovecraft.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unveil the fates of 14 unique playable characters, and choose your path through a pool of 20 dreadful investigations. <br></li><li>Most mysteries harbor multiple endings - for those that survive long enough.<br></li><li>A haunting chiptune soundtrack accentuates the game\u2019s stark 1-bit art style, drawn 100% in MS Paint.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/913740/extras/WOHstorewashi-export.png?t=1730740660\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/913740/page_bg_generat